additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Each capsule contains: Lactobacillus acidophilus (La14) 14 billion cfu, Bifidobacterium lactis (Bl04) 14 billion cfu, HOWARU - Bifidobacterium lactis (HN019) 2 billion cfu (Total Probiotics 30 billion cfu), Inulin 30mg.

additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Drink plenty of water. Do not use when abdominal pain, nausea or vomiting are present or if you develop diarrhoea. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding - seek the advice of a health professional before taking this product. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional.
